	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P78_is_identified_by> "mamhǝr Salomon is a young but famous of scholar of andǝmta. He was born in Bibugn waradā and grew up attending different traditional schools. He studied andǝmta from Dimma and later from mamhǝr Gabra Sǝllasse, till the scholar's death who was the only exsisting scholar of andǝmta who is versed in the lay bet tradition. Memher Solomon attended seminars at St. Paul Seminary in Addis Ababa. In 2011 he was teaching andǝmta at Dabra Mārqos in East Gojjam." .
<https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14017Salomon> <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/P4_has_time_span> _:a13d212c2d1aebb61dec0a4b1a9a2d47 ;
